{
  "stem": "27129.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Aaron, in the meantime, he, he got into a labor camp, because he was inducted in a, in a labor army.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because foreigners they didn't take in the, into the regular army, just to the labor army where they could help out, you know, to, to dig ditches, you know, on the front line or whatever, you know, they could do.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or they did the factories where they need workers because people were taken to the regular army, and they worked in a factory in [NON-ENGLISH], and they had it very tough, very hard, hard work.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not in a, in a camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were-- I say 'they,' it was my cousin and other friends, you know, that they lived there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They, they, they inducted them, and they thought that they going into the regular army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Russian.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in Russia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were surprised that they put them in, in the working army, trud army, they called it. 'Trud' is, is working.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They wanted to go and fight the Germans, you see.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they were looking out to get out, you know, and be free and work again like, like they used to.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they got together, and they-- that was in a very, very remote place, you know, where they, they used to work in a factory where they made pig iron, you know, and they have to carry the, that pig iron, you know, and load up barges, you know, and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother was a barber.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So anyway, they got together, and they're going to get out of there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They thought it's a joke to get out of there.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
